&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**THIS VACANCY IS ONLY OPEN TO EMPLOYEES OF WORCESTERSHIRE ACUTE HOSPITALS NHS TRUST**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A unique and exciting opportunity has arisen for a developmental and rotational band 6 (junior sister) post within the Neonatal Unit and Transitional Care Unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This new concept will encourage the development and leadership skills of existing senior staff nurses. Educational support and coaching will be given throughout the 6 month secondment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you are interested in this internal post and want more information then please contact ward manager Anya Wright on extension 30188 or by email at anya.wright@nhs.net.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
